text: Zheng Jiaqi (born January 13, 1988) is an American table tennis player. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics as part of the American team in the women's team event. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:American female table tennis players Category:American sportspeople of Chinese descent Category:Olympic table tennis players of the United States Category:Table tennis players at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games medalists in table tennis Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for the United States Category:Table tennis players from Shandong Category:People from Zaozhuang Category:Naturalised table tennis players Category:Table tennis players at the 2015 Pan American Games
